#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.31"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.31:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.31:0.2"
msgid "4. Cakkavagga"
msgstr "4. Situations"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.31:0.3"
msgid "31. Cakkasutta"
msgstr "31. Situations"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli2.32"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.31:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, cakkāni, yehi samannāgatānaṃ devamanussānaṃ "
"catucakkaṃ vattati, yehi samannāgatā devamanussā nacirasseva mahantattaṃ "
"vepullattaṃ pāpuṇanti bhogesu."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these four situations. When these situations come "
"about, any god or human who takes advantage of them will soon acquire great "
"and abundant wealth."

msgctxt "an4.31:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

#. VAR: sappurisāvassayo → sappurisūpassayo (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.31:1.3"
msgid ""
"Patirūpadesavāso, sappurisāvassayo, attasammāpaṇidhi, pubbe ca katapuññatā—"
msgstr ""
"Living in a suitable region, relying on good people, right determination, "
"and past merit."

msgctxt "an4.31:1.4"
msgid ""
"imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri cakkāni, yehi samannāgatānaṃ devamanussānaṃ "
"catucakkaṃ vattati, yehi samannāgatā devamanussā nacirasseva mahantattaṃ "
"vepullattaṃ pāpuṇanti bhogesūti."
msgstr ""
"These are the four situations. When these situations come about, any god or "
"human who takes advantage of them will soon acquire great and abundant "
"wealth."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.1"
msgid "Patirūpe vase dese,"
msgstr "When a person lives in a suitable region,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.2"
msgid "ariyamittakaro siyā;"
msgstr "making friends with noble ones,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.3"
msgid "Sammāpaṇidhisampanno,"
msgstr "possessing right determination,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.4"
msgid "pubbe puññakato naro;"
msgstr "and having merit from the past,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.5"
msgid "Dhaññaṃ dhanaṃ yaso kitti,"
msgstr "grain, riches, fame, reputation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.31:2.6"
msgid "sukhañcetaṃdhivattatī”ti."
msgstr "and happiness come to them.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.31:2.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
